---
const repo = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_GISCUS_REPO;
const repoId = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_GISCUS_REPO_ID;
const category = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_GISCUS_CATEGORY;
const categoryId = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_GISCUS_CATEGORY_ID;
const isConfigured = Boolean(repo && repoId && category && categoryId);
const repoSettingsUrl = 'https://github.com/emptyinkpot/emptyinkpot.github.io/settings';
const giscusConfigUrl = 'https://giscus.app/zh-CN';
---

<section class="glass-card rounded-[2rem] p-6">
  <p class="section-kicker mb-3">Feedback</p>
  {
    isConfigured ? (
      <>
        <p class="max-w-3xl text-sm leading-7 text-stone-600">
          评论系统使用 giscus，基于 GitHub Discussions。你可以直接用 GitHub 账号参与讨论和 reactions。
        </p>
        <div class="giscus mt-6"></div>
        <script
          is:inline
          src="https://giscus.app/client.js"
          data-repo={repo}
          data-repo-id={repoId}
          data-category={category}
          data-category-id={categoryId}
          data-mapping="pathname"
          data-strict="0"
          data-reactions-enabled="1"
          data-emit-metadata="0"
          data-input-position="bottom"
          data-theme="preferred_color_scheme"
          data-lang="zh-CN"
          crossorigin="anonymous"
          async
        ></script>
      </>
    ) : (
      <div class="space-y-3 text-sm leading-7 text-stone-600">
        <p>giscus 组件骨架已经接好，但当前仓库侧配置还没完成，所以评论区暂时不会真正加载。</p>
        <p>
          要真正启用它，先去
          <a class="underline decoration-[rgba(31,74,95,0.3)] underline-offset-4" href={repoSettingsUrl} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">仓库设置</a>
          开启 Discussions，再到
          <a class="underline decoration-[rgba(31,74,95,0.3)] underline-offset-4" href={giscusConfigUrl} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">giscus 配置页</a>
          生成 `PUBLIC_GISCUS_*` 参数。
        </p>
        <p>变量模板已经放在 `site-v2/.env.example`，补齐后重新构建即可直接启用。</p>
      </div>
    )
  }
</section>
